description: Tanya Thomas started small by renting out single rooms to treat clients one-on-one. As word spread, her waitlist grew to three months, leading her to open Tanya Thomas Skin Clinic in midtown Manhattan in 2021. With support from American Express, Tanya manages her growing business while still taking the time to treat each client like royalty. #ad
